imdb.plot outline: Strange things begin happening to Sawyer Chambers after she wakes up in her dorm room without recollection of how she got there. Haunted by mysterious dreams and the stranger who has a familiarity as he appears to her, she begins therapy to try and piece together fragments of what happened during a camping trip with her friends. Sawyer Struggles with becoming who she wants to be, but the real question is...what is she?
